    <activity>
        <statement>

            <p>
                <term>Work in Groups to:</term>
            </p>

            <p>
                Identify and record items in your environment that are commonly bought through hire purchase. Discuss why people prefer hire purchase instead of paying cash.
            </p>

            <tabular top="medium" bottom="medium" right="medium" left="medium">
                <row header="yes">
                    <cell>Item</cell>
                    <cell>Reason for Hire Purchase</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Television</cell>
                    <cell>High cost makes full payment difficult</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                </row>
            </tabular>

            <p>
                <alert>In your groups explore the situation below:</alert>
            </p>

            <p>
                A shop sells a television on hire purchase under the following terms:
            </p>

            <p>
                Cash price = Ksh <m>40,000</m>, Deposit = Ksh <m>10,000</m>, Monthly instalment = Ksh <m>2,500</m> for <m>14</m> months.
            </p>

            <p>
                <alert>In your groups you are required to:</alert>
            </p>

            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Calculate the total amount paid through hire purchase.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Determine the extra cost paid compared to the cash price.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Express the extra cost as a fraction of the cash price.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Convert the fraction into a percentage.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <alert>Further Exploration:</alert> Compare the total cost of buying an item using cash and hire purchase. Discuss the advantages and disadvantages of each method.
            </p>

            <p>
                Explore what happens if the repayment period increases or decreases.
            </p>
        </statement>
    </activity>

